thread.title: Wendy
thread.title_full: Fast Cover Travel Insurance reviewed by Wendy

author: Wendy
title: Wendy
text: Although we have not had our travels yet, I cannot comment on any claims. But the process to apply online was extremely fast and easy to follow. Also a lot cheaper than others for the same coverage. They covered us even though we are now seniors, as some other insurers would not. So far very happy customers.
